## Model Configuration

### Random Forest
| Parameter | Value |
|---|---|
| Estimators | 200 |
| Max depth | 20 |
| Min samples split | 5 |
| Min samples leaf | 2 |
| Class weight | balanced |

### XGBoost
| Parameter | Value |
|---|---|
| Estimators | 300 |
| Max depth | 8 |
| Learning rate | 0.05 |
| Subsample | 0.8 |
| Column sample | 0.8 |
| Evaluation metric | mlogloss |

### LSTM
| Parameter | Value |
|---|---|
| LSTM layers | 2 (128 + 64 units) |
| Dropout | 0.2 |
| Dense layer | 64 units ReLU |
| Output layer | 4 units Softmax |
| Epochs | 20 |
| Batch size | 256 |
| Optimiser | Adam |
| Loss function | Categorical crossentropy |

