## Class Balancing

SMOTE (Synthetic Minority Oversampling Technique) was applied
to the training partition only to address class imbalance.

Original class distribution:
| AQI Category | Proportion |
|---|---|
| Low | ~68% |
| Moderate | ~21% |
| High | ~9% |
| Very High | ~2% |

After SMOTE: equal distribution across all four classes.
